COMPONENT NAME: LKM SQL to Hive SQOOP COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.3.0.1 and above DESCRIPTION: This KM integrates data from a JDBC data source into Hive It executes the following steps: 1. Create a Hive staging table 2. Create a SQOOP configuration file, which contains the upstream query. 3. Execute SQOOP to extract the source data and import into Hive 4. Drop the Hive staging table This is a direct load LKM and must be used without any IKM. Additional information can be found in the KM option descriptions.
Please see BigDataConnector Documentation for more details.
